description: A "Celebration of Life" was held on Wednesday to remember the three women who died at a veterans center in Yountville. Here's a look at the speakers at the memorial service.
maintext: The Veterans Health Administration Executive in Charge Dr. Carolyn Clancy spoke at the memorial for the Yountville shooting victims, saying she knows the three victims would want those who serve veterans to carry on this important work with honor and pride as they did.
title: VIDEO: Speakers at memorial for Yountville shooting victims
